8, \"to\": 383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"First of all, the Vatican does not identify the perpetrators behind this offense [ LGBT drag queens] nor does it cite the nature of the offense [blasphemous attack on the Last Supper].\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 469, \"end\": 473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT\", \"score\": 0.9953897550523712, \"rank\": 0.004500711386077962, \"text\": \"LGBT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Vatican\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 411}, {\"ngram\": \"the perpetrators\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"this offense\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 466}, {\"ngram\": \"the nature\", \"from\": 504, \"to\": 514}, {\"ngram\": \"the offense\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 529}, {\"ngram\": \"blasphemous attack\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 549}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why the silence?\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 587, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Why the silence\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 586}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While admitting the event was wrong, Rome is exploiting it to suggest that we dignify other religions.\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 626, \"end\": 630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holy_See\", \"score\": 0.9043321671871478, \"rank\": 0.10578832468278304, \"text\": \"Rome\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holy_See\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holy_See\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 614}, {\"ngram\": \"other religions\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The statement emphasizes that we should not offend \\\"believers of other religions\\\" but fails to mention that the Olympics ceremony offended God.\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 835, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The statement\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 705}, {\"ngram\": \"believers\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 753}, {\"ngram\": \"other religions\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics ceremony\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nor does it mention that the devotees of the Last Supper - the world's Catholics - were the ones targeted by this attack.\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 957, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 907, \"end\": 916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999999993683559, \"rank\": 6.072645244008043e-10, \"text\": \"Catholics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the devotees\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 873}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 892}, {\"ngram\": \"the ones\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 932}, {\"ngram\": \"this attack\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"*Other religions do not have devotion to the Last Supper.\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other religions\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"devotion\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 995}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1014}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The statement continues: Allusions?\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The statement\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"Allusions\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The attack on the Last Supper was a blatant, malicious, and deliberate commission of blasphemy against the Catholic Church.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999999998581188, \"rank\": 1.1584827723664207e-10, \"text\": \"Catholic Church\"