hrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this public blasphemy\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The committee'sfake apologyof \\\"inclusion\\\" and \\\"diversity\\\" holds no water.\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1490, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The committee'sfake apologyof \\\"inclusion\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1457}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"diversity\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"no water\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1489}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Vatican statement added: Not necessarily.\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1538, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Vatican statement\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If the expression is one of goodness and truth there are no limits, even if it offends the whole world.\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the expression\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1556}, {\"ngram\": \"goodness\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1575}, {\"ngram\": \"truth\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"no limits\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1605}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole world\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Catholic truth 'offends' most religions, so should we tone it down for them out of 'respect?'\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1643, \"end\": 1651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999995853828245, \"rank\": 4.143942915127959e-07, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Romesupportsand is careful about not offending LGBT \\\"convictions\\\" but has no problem insulting Roman Catholic convictions.\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1859, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1784, \"end\": 1788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT\", \"score\": 0.9953897550523712, \"rank\": 0.004500711386077962, \"text\": \"LGBT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT\"}, {\"begin\": 1832, \"end\": 1846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999999999731699, \"rank\": 2.667204566983117e-11, \"text\": \"Roman Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Romesupportsand\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1752}, {\"ngram\": \"no problem\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In short, the Vatican statement is an evasive, half-baked response to the Olympics' obscene attack on the Last Supper.\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1979, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Vatican statement\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1892}, {\"ngram\": \"an evasive, half-baked response\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics' obscene attack\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1959}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 1978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It does not decry this abomination that offended God and that made a laughingstock of His Church.\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 2077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this abomination\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2014}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"a laughingstock\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"His Church\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rome should at least admonish the satanic LGBT group that waged this attack, but Francis refuses to do this.\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2187, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2079, \"end\": 2083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holy_See\", \"score\": 0.9043321671871478, \"rank\": 0.10578832468278304, \"text\": \"Rome\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holy_See\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holy_See\"}, {\"begin\": 2121, \"end\": 2125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT\", \"score\": 0.9953897550523712, \"rank\": 0.004500711386077962, \"text\": \"LGBT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT\"}, {\"begin\": 2160, \"end\": 2167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.827035917562317e-12, \"text\": \"Francis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19546\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this attack\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is against the idea of correcting homosexuals.\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2237, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2210}, {\"ngram\": \"homosexuals\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is quick to \\\"correct\\\" those who admonish them but willnever correctthe real offenders.\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2327, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"real offenders\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This raises serious questions.\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"serious questions\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"* We should not rule out that the perpetrators of this obscene \\\"Last Supper\\\" not only attempted to profane the Last Supper but were putting across the message that the Last Supper is what offends other religions.\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2573, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the perpetrators\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2407}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Last Supper\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2436}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2483}, {\"ngram\": \"the mess